snippet.title: Johnny & Amber | Body Language Explained | The Final Word and Insane Behavioral Insight
snippet.description:
Welcome back to the follow up! and part 1 of 2 so I can make sure you can digest all the details. Here we take a further look at the behavioural insight and what can be gleaned from reading these people. Addressing the questions you guys have been asking in the comments from the previous videos. Time to clear up once and for all whose camp I think you should be in. All 2 cents welcome. Looking at the details through the eyes of a people reader and coming to the truth at the end.

Don’t forget to subscribe to my newsletter through my website https://www.bencardall.com 

You can support the channel and get your own copy of The Monographs here: https://linktr.ee/bencardall 

https://www.bencardall.com/1-on-1-coaching/ contact me for further details 

Don’t be strangers 

Ben x Talking about johnny & amber
